name: Comparative Nutritional Analysis of Fast Food vs. Regular Food
description: An exploratory data analysis project comparing macronutrient and micronutrient profiles of fast food items against standard USDA food items to identify key health differentiators. The analysis identifies Sodium Density and Fat Consistency as primary distinguishing factors between the two groups.
